data.description: Check out this beautiful craftsman-style home with farmhouse details. Located at the base of wolf-ridge hill, this cozy home features 1,552 sq. ft. with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms in a split floor plan. The home boasts elegant granite countertops providing a stylish and functional space, and vinyl plank flooring with a walk-in closet. The property has a wooden privacy fence, an attached 2-car garage, and stainless steel appliances included. This house also has excellent views of the world's highest hill making every moment in this home a picturesque experience!
